# Google Maps SDK for Android API key.
# Required for Android map tiles to render (react-native-maps).
# iOS uses Apple Maps by default and needs no key.
#
# Get one: Google Cloud Console -> APIs & Services -> Credentials,
# with "Maps SDK for Android" enabled on the project.
#
# For local dev-client builds: put this in a local .env (gitignored)
# or export it in your shell before running `expo prebuild` / `expo run:android`.
# For EAS cloud builds: eas secret:create --name GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY --value <key>
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
